| Column Name | Data Type           | Description                                                                                                                                                                                               |
| ----------- | ------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Year        | Integer (`int64`)   | Reporting year for the greenhouse gas emissions record. Used for time-series trend analysis and forecasting.                                                                                              |
| Provinces   | Text (`object`)     | Name of the Canadian province or territory associated with the emissions data. Used for province-level comparisons and regional analysis.                                                                 |
| Emissions   | Decimal (`float64`) | Greenhouse gas emissions value measured in kilotonnes of carbon dioxide equivalent (kt CO₂e). Used for KPI calculations, trend analysis, and Power BI visualizations.                                     |
| Sectors     | Text (`object`)     | Economic or industrial sector responsible for the reported emissions (e.g., transportation, agriculture, electricity generation, manufacturing). Used for sector-level emissions analysis and breakdowns. |
